### Analytics Service API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7006
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get All Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Analytics by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Analytics Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Financial Summary (Current Month)
@startDate = 2024-10-01
@endDate = 2024-10-31
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/summary?startDate={{startDate}}&endDate={{endDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Expenses by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/categories?startDate={{startDate}}&endDate={{endDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Spending Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/trends?period=Monthly&months=12
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Analytics by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/range?startDate={{startDate}}&endDate={{endDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Analytics
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-10-09",
  "totalExpenses": 500.00,
  "totalIncome": 2000.00,
  "totalSavings": 300.00,
  "budgetUtilization": 80.5,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "categoryName": "Food & Dining",
  "categoryAmount": 150.00,
  "period": "Monthly"
}

### Update Analytics
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-10-09",
  "totalExpenses": 550.00,
  "totalIncome": 2000.00,
  "totalSavings": 350.00,
  "budgetUtilization": 85.0,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "categoryName": "Food & Dining",
  "categoryAmount": 175.00,
  "period": "Monthly"
}

### Generate Analytics
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2024-10-09",
  "period": "Daily"
}

### Get Health Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/health-status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Analytics
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Analytics by Period (Query Parameter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics?period=Monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}